      • addDynamicCounter

        public boolean addDynamicCounter(String key,
                        Callable<Long> valueProducer)
        Sets the dynamic counter if a counter with the specified key doesn't already exist
        Parameters:
        key - the key for the dynamic counter
        valueProducer - the generator value for this counter
        Returns:
        true if the counter was added. False, if a counter with the specified key exists already

      • removeDynamicCounter

        public boolean removeDynamicCounter(String key)
        Removes a dynamic counter with the specified key
        Parameters:
        key - the key for the dynamic counter
        Returns:
        true if a counter with the specified key existed and was removed, false otherwise.
